Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:27.31,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn@DFHanziPenW5-A\frz270\c&H050303&\pos(484.27,405.33)}海野亭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.32,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZLanTingHei-R-GBK\c&H424040&\frz17.5\pos(586.22,284.45)}老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:12.15,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\bord2}家裡在維修\N不能住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:12.15,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\bord2}\N這樣啊…\N那可真夠受的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:12.15,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\bord2}\N…所以想問問您\N能不能再把房子\N借我暫住幾天？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.15,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\bord2}\N你隨意住吧\N沒問題的
